statement:
SELECT * FROM (     SELECT CASE              WHEN t0.v3 THEN t2.v2             WHEN s0.v3 THEN '123'             ELSE t2.v3         END AS x0, t1.v1     FROM s0          JOIN t0 ON s0.v2 = t0.v2         JOIN t1 ON s0.v2 = t1.v2 OR s0.v3 = t1.v2
       JOIN t2 ON t1.v2 = t2.v2     WHERE t2.v1 = 2 ) temp WHERE x0 > 1;
